# textdomain: mcl_totems
Totem of Undying=Totem nesmrtnosti
Protects you from death while wielding it=Ščiti vas pred smrtjo, medtem ko ga držite
A totem of undying is a rare artifact which may safe you from certain death.=Totem nesmrtnosti je redek artefakt, ki vas lahko reši pred gotovo smrtjo.
The totem only works while you hold it in your hand. If you receive fatal damage, you are saved from death and you get a second chance with 1 HP. The totem is destroyed in the process, however.=Totem deluje le, ko ga držite v roki. Če prejmete usodno škodo, ste rešeni pred smrtjo in dobite drugo priložnost z 1 točko zdravja. Vendar se totem v postopku uniči.